works.description:
This is Mahalaxmi Siddh Charan Paduka.  
This item you can purchase only near dipawali and in Diwali night with
that  
charan you have to perform mahalaxmi mahamantra prayog once. After that  
place this Mahalaxmi charan paduka at worship place of home. daily show  
incense stick and also light one ghee lamp near charan paduka. This  
Mahalaxmi Siddh Charan Paduka is energized for balanced of money and
wealth  
in life. Mahalaxmi Siddh Charan Paduka gives balance of wealth and  
prosperity in life. If in your life you are facing financial problems,  
money crisis and Loan you have, your earning is good but saving is nil so 

place this item, your money will not go anywhere and daily and daily you  

will earn more and more money in life. Mahalaxmi Siddh Charan Paduka will 

place Mahalaxmi permanently at home she will not leave your home forever.

This item available free of cost with Dhanlaxmi Kuber Dhanwarsha Yantra
